 * group:content => 内容设置
 * content.badge => 徽章文字:text:App Download
 * content.title => 标题:text:Android access designed for clarity
 * content.description => 描述:textarea:Use the app to check schedules, save favorite markets, and review formats with a clean interface.
 * 
 * group:download => 下载设置
 * download.title => 下载标题:text:Choose the preferred download path
 * download.description => 下载描述:textarea:Get the official Android build with clear release notes and version labeling.
 * download.primary_text => 主下载按钮:text:Primary Download
 * download.primary_url => 主下载链接:text:#
 * download.secondary_text => 帮助按钮:text:Need Help?
