 * group:features => 特性列表
 * features.items => 特性列表:textarea:Lightweight install\r\nResult history\r\nMarket reminders|一行一个特性
 * 
 * group:checklist => 安装清单
 * checklist.title => 清单标题:text:Quick install checklist
 * checklist.items => 清单项目:textarea:Confirm the source|Use official download links and verify the app name before installing\r\nAllow install prompts|Enable installation for trusted sources only when prompted\r\nReview permissions|Check notifications and storage access before you confirm|格式：标题|描述，一行一个
 * 
 * @fields_end
